test_unit_memory_maintenance
  record_type "meta_test"
  suite "memory_maintenance"
  test_file "tests/unit/memory_maintenance.rs"
  pins "plan_memory_dreaming, apply_dreaming_plan, classify_event, usage_counts, duplicate_key, required_reclaim_bytes, event_topic, requirement_statement, learn_from_memory, replay_candidate_tasks, mine_patterns, apply_retained_amendments, measure_storage, persist_auto_free_space_choice, and run_core_dreaming_once: duplicate restructuring by recalculated use, raw/learning protection, requires_bigger_storage reporting, topic-frequency recalculation, durable-requirement learning, amendment generalization, covered-specific forgetting under pressure, and idempotent amendment materialization."
